Hello, for those interested, here our YouTube channel with the launch of our monthly program "Hello Startups" presented by Alexandra Muraton and produced by Christel Piriou (Rue de la Prod). Both professional audiovisual co-created this concept to highlight Start up 5 new French emission interviewing founders followed the advice of an expert. Investors, entrepreneurs, self-taught, students and enthusiasts, follow us by subscribing to our channel!
It all started with an observation: a benchmark has enabled us to see that there was no offer of interesting and inexpensive for French start-up in video. It is nevertheless essential to develop an entrepreneurial project.
The solution: a web TV channel to start up with the sharing of costs of a day of shooting between the different participating startups.
